Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:45.78,Thoughts,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Droga, eu não consigo nem falar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:50.03,Main,Sai,0,0,0,,Ei, Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:57.94,Main,Sai,0,0,0,,Ouça!\NO Vovô tem algo pra dizer a você.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:01.06,Main,Boo,0,0,0,,Aguente firme, vovô!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:04.70,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Que? Me deixa em paz! Eu te venci de forma justa!
